ootnotes":""},"categories":[4],"tags":[416,361,400,114,230,20,105,295,293,32],"class_list":["post-19432","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-righteousness-al-birr","tag-agreed-upon-muttafaqun-alayhi","tag-bowing-al-ruku","tag-dawn-prayer-salat-fajr","tag-manners-adab","tag-night-prayer-al-tahajjud","tag-prayer-al-salat","tag-ramadan","tag-voluntary-prayers-salat-nafilah","tag-witr-prayer","tag-worship-al-ibadah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-53q","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":28132,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/nawafil-witr-sunan-fajr\/","url_meta":{"origin":19432,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Praying Witr prayer, Sunan of dawn prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would pray at night, two by two, and make it odd with one cycle. The Prophet would pray two cycles before the morning prayer, so lightly as if the call to prayer were in his ears. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28161,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/make-your-last-prayer-witr\/","url_meta":{"origin":19432,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Witr: Make last prayer at night Witr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cMake the last of your prayers at night the Witr prayer.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 998, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 751 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28159,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/witr-beginning-middle-end\/","url_meta":{"origin":19432,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Witr: The Prophet prays Witr before dawn","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would perform Witr prayer every night, either at the beginning, middle, or end of the night, finishing his Witr prayer before the break of dawn. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 996, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 745 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28163,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/pray-witr-before-morning\/","url_meta":{"origin":19432,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Pray Witr before morning comes","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPerform Witr prayer before the morning.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 754 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0648\u0652\u062a\u0650\u0631\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0642\u064e\u0628\u0652\u0644\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062a\u064f\u0635\u0652\u0628\u0650\u062d\u064f\u0648\u0627 754 \u0635\u062d\u064a\u062d \u0645\u0633\u0644\u0645 \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628 \u0635\u0644\u0627\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0633\u0627\u0641\u0631\u064a\u0646 \u0648\u0642\u0635\u0631\u0647\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43018,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/11\/night-time-routine\/","url_meta":{"origin":19432,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Tahajjud: The Prophet\u2019s night-time routine","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 11, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would pray eleven cycles in the night. When dawn arrived, he would pray two brief cycles, then lie on his right side until the caller came to announce the prayer. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6310, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 736 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25408,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/11\/three-regular-practices\/","url_meta":{"origin":19432,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Worship: The Prophet advises three practices","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 11, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: My dear friend the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, advised me to do three deeds and I will never abandon them until I die: to fast three days of every month, to perform forenoon prayer, and to sleep after performing the Witr prayer. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/19432","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=19432"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/19432\/revisions"}],"wp:attach